import React from 'react'
import FlexStyled from '../styled/Flex'
import FlexCard from '../styled/FlexCard'
import Grid from '../styled/Grid'
import GridChild from '../styled/GridChild'
import LoginImage from '../resources/login.svg'

function Login() {
  return (
      <FlexStyled
          direction="column"
          justify="center"
          align="center"
          height="100%"
          wrap="nowrap"
          
      >

          <FlexCard>
          <Grid
                  templatecolumns='1fr 1fr'
                  templaterows='1fr'
              >

                  <GridChild rowstart={1} rowend={2} columnstart={2} columnend={3} >
                      
                  </GridChild>

              </Grid>
              
         </FlexCard>

    </FlexStyled>
  )
}

export default Login
